results.name: Values of w(k) when w(k-2), w(k-1), and w(k) are all odd, where w is A336957.
comment: It would be nice to understand what is special about these numbers. The majority of them appear to products of two distinct primes. There seems to be very little overlap with either A337646 or A338057, although 1531513 appears both here and in A337646.
